text: Nurnisa Abbas is a Uyghur musician known for Uyghur opera music. She also currently serves as a judge on the reality talent show The Voice of the Silk Road. ==References== Category:Uyghur music Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Uyghur people Category:Chinese female singers Category:21st-century Chinese women singers
